devdoc.author: Peter Brooke
devdoc.details: Multi-item aucton contract    The auction system should allow users to place bids on items and automatically determine the highest bidder when the auction ends.    The smart contract should have the following functionality:    1. Initialise the auction with a list of items and their starting bids.    2. Allow users to place bids on items.    3. Automatically determine the highest bidder for each item when the auction ends.
